example_evaluator_prompt.user:
## Query
Query ID: {query_id}
Persona: {persona}
Production system: {production_system}
Query text: "{query_text}"

## MWS Variable Values (summary)
{mws_variable_summary_json}

## Response to Evaluate
{diagnosis_response_json}

## Rubric
{evaluation_rubric_json}

## Instructions
1. Score each dimension D1–D6 (0–3) with a one-sentence justification citing specific fields from the response.
2. Check all error flags (EF1–EF5) and list any triggered.
3. Apply the persona-specific weight adjustment if applicable.
4. Compute weighted_total = sum(score_i * effective_weight_i / 3) - sum(flag penalties), floored at 0.
5. Write a 2–3 sentence summary.
6. Output only valid JSON conforming to the evaluator_output_schema.
